#Linux user management ####

# User account management 

commands 
useradd 
groupadd
userdel
groupdel
usermod

Files

/etc/passwd
/etc/group
/etc/shadow

Example :

useradd km445
id km445
cd /home/
ls

groupadd superheros
userdel -r spiderman
groupadd nonnewgroup
groupdel nonnewgroup

usermod -aG spiderman  km445
cat /etc/group |grep km445

chgrp -R superheros km445

